{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>About Abyss Online</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on an epic adventure in <strong>Abyss Online</strong>, the <strong>newest PVP MMORPG</strong> releasing in <strong>2025</strong>. Dive into a vast <strong>open-world</strong> teeming with possibilities, where a <strong>player-driven economy</strong> and intense <strong>PVP battles</strong> shape your destiny.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Early Access Disclaimer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Abyss Online is currently in Early Access and is under active development. While not yet feature-complete, we're continuously expanding the game with new content and systems. Please note that major updates may require game resets. Your feedback is invaluable in shaping the future of Abyss Online.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Expansive Open World</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore diverse landscapes from bustling towns to untamed wilderness.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Player-Driven Economy</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Influence the market through gathering, crafting, and trading.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Intense PVP Combat</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage in arena battles against other players and rise to the top.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Evolving World</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Encounter dynamic events and challenges that react to player actions.</p></li></ul></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Early Access Highlights</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Starter Zone Exploration</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Begin your journey in a rich starter zone filled with resources and secrets.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gathering and Crafting</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect materials to craft weapons, armor, and tools essential for survival.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Mob Camps and Combat</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Test your skills against challenging mobs and earn valuable loot.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Community-Driven Development</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Participate in shaping the game by providing feedback and suggestions.</p></li></ul></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Planned Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dynamic Building Mechanics</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Construct and customize structures in the open world.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>New Regions and Biomes</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock new areas with unique environments and creatures.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Enhanced Quest System</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience deeper storytelling and engaging missions.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Advanced PVP Mechanics</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Introducing guild wars, territory control, and ranked arenas.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Expanded Crafting and Skills</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">More crafting options and skill trees for character customization.</p></li></ul></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Join Our Community</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Become a part of the <strong>Abyss Online</strong> community! Share your experiences, discuss strategies, and collaborate with fellow adventurers. Your insights help us create a game that evolves with its players.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Discord:</strong> Join our Discord server</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Social Media:</strong> Follow us on Twitter, Facebook, and Instagram.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Stay Updated</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Wishlist and Follow Abyss Online</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Add the game to your wishlist and follow us on Steam to receive the latest updates and announcements.</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Experience the next generation of PVP MMORPGs with Abyss Online. Your adventure awaits!</strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493960/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732891889","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493960/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1732891889","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493960/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732891889","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493960/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1732891889","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"MMO","id":20},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"This is an open world fantasy MMORPG, sometimes there will be blood when a character is injured and players can kill other players in open world or arena PvP combat. \r\n\r\nMost of the mature content will be in the in general chat of our game."},"detailed_description":"<h1>Join Us On Discord</h1><p>","developers":["Old World Labs"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"2